{
  "name": "postmark-world",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "The told world of Postmark — the semantic-world engine (heightfield, field-of-view, LOD, radial serializer) and its spine verbs (orient / open-your-eyes / investigate / walk). Browser-pure: the site computes FOV client-side from the public world-state.json + skeleton.json, read-only by construction.",
